<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-1168] HTTPClient doesn&apos;t send authentication header in threaded environment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1168</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>Using HTTPClient with multiple threads and basic authentication seems to create a race condition. The request headers sometimes don&amp;#39;t contain the authorization entry, which results in a 401 (although the username and password credentials are correctly set). </description>
